"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933644-bbc-gabby-logan-paris-olympics-theory\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  BBC presenterGabby Loganhas cast doubt over the winner's bell at theParis 2024 Olympics, a revered tradition in athletics events.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9993814989055196, \"rank\": 0.000459746861080242, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bell is typically rung by winners of events, however, the 51-year-old spotted a potential issue with the timing of the bell during the celebrations.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident occurred when Sweden's pole-vaulting champion Armand Duplantis triumphantly rang the bell after securing his gold medal.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999500145824038, \"rank\": 1.972583471167662e-05, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharing her skepticism, Gabby said: \\\"Now, I have noticed this, that the bell starts to ring before the timer actually calls the bell.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hoping, I am not seeing..\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like Santa Claus.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2018041482447946e-17, \"text\": \"Santa Claus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is that what I am seeing?\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is this a bit of theatre going on down there?\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", she openly pondered.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BBCpundit and tAmerican sprinter Michael Johnson, jested that perhaps his co-star was just eager for a chance to ring the bell herself.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To which Gabby humorously responded: \\\"We will be investigating that, and maybe send you down, Michael.\\\"\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Team GB disqualified from Olympics sailing event but still have chance of gold    She added firmly: \\\"In the name of good journalism I want to make sure that that bell is real.\\\"\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tradition dictates that each gold medalist at the Stade de France is afforded the privilege of ringing the bell, which, following the Games, will find a new home at the iconic Notre Dame cathedral    It comes afterGabby bravely opened up about her personal health struggles.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to